) AS [t]

) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[UserId]

INTO @inserted0;

INNER JOIN @inserted0 i ON ([t].[Id] = [i].[Id])
ORDER BY [i].[_Position];

(DbType = Int32)], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[ConcurrencyStamp], [t].[CreationTime], [t].[CreatorUserId], [t].[DeleterUserId], [t].[DeletionTime], [t].[Description], [t].[DisplayName], [t].[IsDefault], [t].[IsDeleted], [t].[IsStatic], [t].[LastModificationTime], [t].[LastModifierUserId], [t].[Name], [t].[NormalizedName], [t].[TenantId], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CreationTime], [t0].[CreatorUserId], [t0].[Discriminator], [t0].[IsGranted], [t0].[Name], [t0].[TenantId], [t0].[RoleId]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(2) [a].[Id], [a].[ConcurrencyStamp], [a].[CreationTime], [a].[CreatorUserId], [a].[DeleterUserId], [a].[DeletionTime], [a].[Description], [a].[DisplayName], [a].[IsDefault], [a].[IsDeleted], [a].[IsStatic], [a].[LastModificationTime], [a].[LastModifierUserId], [a].[Name], [a].[NormalizedName], [a].[TenantId]
    FROM [AbpRoles] AS [a]
    WHERE (((@__ef_filter__p_0 = CAST(1 AS bit)) OR ([a].[IsDeleted] <> CAST(1 AS bit))) AND ((@__ef_filter__p_1 = CAST(1 AS bit)) OR ([a].[TenantId] = @__ef_filter__CurrentTenantId_2))) AND ([a].[Name] = N'Center Manager')
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a0].[Id], [a0].[CreationTime], [a0].[CreatorUserId], [a0].[Discriminator], [a0].[IsGranted], [a0].[Name], [a0].[TenantId], [a0].[RoleId]
    FROM [AbpPermissions] AS [a0]
    WHERE ([a0].[Discriminator] = N'RolePermissionSetting') AND ((@__ef_filter__p_3 = CAST(1 AS bit)) OR ([a0].[TenantId] = @__ef_filter__CurrentTenantId_4))
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[RoleId]

    SELECT TOP(2) [a].[Id], [a].[ConcurrencyStamp], [a].[CreationTime], [a].[CreatorUserId], [a].[DeleterUserId], [a].[DeletionTime], [a].[Description], [a].[DisplayName], [a].[IsDefault], [a].[IsDeleted], [a].[IsStatic], [a].[LastModificationTime], [a].[LastModifierUserId], [a].[Name], [a].[NormalizedName], [a].[TenantId]

    WHERE (((@__ef_filter__p_0 = CAST(1 AS bit)) OR ([a].[IsDeleted] <> CAST(1 AS bit))) AND ((@__ef_filter__p_1 = CAST(1 AS bit)) OR ([a].[TenantId] = @__ef_filter__CurrentTenantId_2))) AND ([a].[Name] = N'Center Manager')
) AS [t]

) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[RoleId]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[ConcurrencyStamp], [t].[CreationTime], [t].[CreatorUserId], [t].[DeleterUserId], [t].[DeletionTime], [t].[Description], [t].[DisplayName], [t].[IsDefault], [t].[IsDeleted], [t].[IsStatic], [t].[LastModificationTime], [t].[LastModifierUserId], [t].[Name], [t].[NormalizedName], [t].[TenantId], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CreationTime], [t0].[CreatorUserId], [t0].[Discriminator], [t0].[IsGranted], [t0].[Name], [t0].[TenantId], [t0].[RoleId]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(2) [a].[Id], [a].[ConcurrencyStamp], [a].[CreationTime], [a].[CreatorUserId], [a].[DeleterUserId], [a].[DeletionTime], [a].[Description], [a].[DisplayName], [a].[IsDefault], [a].[IsDeleted], [a].[IsStatic], [a].[LastModificationTime], [a].[LastModifierUserId], [a].[Name], [a].[NormalizedName], [a].[TenantId]
    FROM [AbpRoles] AS [a]
    WHERE (((@__ef_filter__p_0 = CAST(1 AS bit)) OR ([a].[IsDeleted] <> CAST(1 AS bit))) AND ((@__ef_filter__p_1 = CAST(1 AS bit)) OR ([a].[TenantId] = @__ef_filter__CurrentTenantId_2))) AND ([a].[Name] = N'Center Manager')
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a0].[Id], [a0].[CreationTime], [a0].[CreatorUserId], [a0].[Discriminator], [a0].[IsGranted], [a0].[Name], [a0].[TenantId], [a0].[RoleId]
    FROM [AbpPermissions] AS [a0]
    WHERE ([a0].[Discriminator] = N'RolePermissionSetting') AND ((@__ef_filter__p_3 = CAST(1 AS bit)) OR ([a0].[TenantId] = @__ef_filter__CurrentTenantId_4))
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[RoleId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id]

FROM [AbpAuditLogs]

    SELECT [a].[Id], [a].[AccessFailedCount], [a].[AddressLine1], [a].[AddressLine2], [a].[AuthenticationSource], [a].[City], [a].[ConcurrencyStamp], [a].[CreationTime], [a].[CreatorUserId], [a].[DeleterUserId], [a].[DeletionTime], [a].[EmailAddress], [a].[EmailConfirmationCode], [a].[Gender], [a].[IsActive], [a].[IsDeleted], [a].[IsEmailConfirmed], [a].[IsLockoutEnabled], [a].[IsPhoneNumberConfirmed], [a].[IsTwoFactorEnabled], [a].[LastModificationTime], [a].[LastModifierUserId], [a].[LockoutEndDateUtc], [a].[Name], [a].[NormalizedEmailAddress], [a].[NormalizedUserName], [a].[Password], [a].[PasswordResetCode], [a].[PhoneNumber], [a].[PostalCode], [a].[ProvinceId], [a].[RegionId], [a].[SecurityStamp], [a].[Surname], [a].[TenantId], [a].[UserName]
    FROM [AbpUsers] AS [a]
    WHERE ((@__ef_filter__p_0 = CAST(1 AS bit)) OR ([a].[IsDeleted] <> CAST(1 AS bit))) AND ((@__ef_filter__p_1 = CAST(1 AS bit)) OR [a].[TenantId] IS NULL)
    ORDER BY [a].[UserName]
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a0].[Id], [a0].[CreationTime], [a0].[CreatorUserId], [a0].[RoleId], [a0].[TenantId], [a0].[UserId]
    FROM [AbpUserRoles] AS [a0]
    WHERE (@__ef_filter__p_3 = CAST(1 AS bit)) OR [a0].[TenantId] IS NULL
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[UserId]
ORDER BY [t].[UserName], [t].[Id], [t0].[Id]

WHEN NOT MATCHED THEN

VALUES (i.[CreationTime], i.[CreatorUserId], i.[Discriminator], i.[IsGranted], i.[Name], i.[RoleId], i.[TenantId])
OUTPUT INSERTED.[Id], i._Position
INTO @inserted0;

INNER JOIN @inserted0 i ON ([t].[Id] = [i].[Id])
ORDER BY [i].[_Position];

FROM [AbpAuditLogs]
WHERE @@ROWCOUNT = 1 AND [Id] = scope_identity();

WHERE ([a].[IsAbandoned] <> CAST(1 AS bit)) AND ([a].[NextTryTime] <= @__Now_0)
ORDER BY [a].[Priority] DESC, [a].[TryCount], [a].[NextTryTime]
